* The estimates are arrangned in rows (different estimators) and columns (set of covariates used) in the table
* Row 1-3 corresponds to ATT on observables and unobservables using the three different set of instruments
* Row 4-5 correspond to ATT using IPW (Hirano), where row 5 also includes age 11 test scores -> Y1 in the current code
* Rows 6-10 correspond to the matching effects (not reported)
